author: Disney
description:
Avatar: Fire and Ash filmmaker James Cameron sits down with TikTok’s Forrest Galante ( @ForrestGalante), a Rare Species Expert, for an in-depth conversation about the design, habits, and biology of Pandora and its creatures.  
 
Explore more about Pandora by searching “Avatar” on TikTok.
 
Avatar: Fire and Ash is now playing only in theatres. Get tickets now.
